/*STARTUPSCRIPT STARTS*/
function StartupScript()
{
stepId = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.route.stepid").value*1;
stepNumber = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.route.stepnumber").value*1;
try
{
sFormStatus = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.hidden.event").value.toLowerCase();
decisionVariable = stepId > 0 ? stepId: sFormStatus;
setUpPrintingAndPublishing();
/* This function call will add Blank Option to all role dropdowns */
SP_InsertBlank();
/* This function call will set visibility of T4 Department Involved*/
SP_ToggleVisibility("lbDeptsInvolved","hlpDeptsInvolved_exclude");
document.getElementById("lbDeptsInvolved").size = document.getElementById("lbDeptsInvolved").length;
/* This function call will put reference of launched CAPA, eMDR and Action Item Forms */
PutLaunchedFormNumber();
/*This function call will display questions in MDR/Adverse Event Evaluation T3 tab*/
ManageEMDRQuestions();
/*This function call will display questions in Vigilance sub tab in T3 tab*/
InitiateVigilanceQuestions();
/*These functions control FTFL icon visibility based on the configuration variables*/
ManageCAPATypeSelection();
ManageEMDRTypeSelection();
/* This function call will display View buttons after FTFL*/
DisplayViewLinksButtons();
/* This function call is used to program onclick event of signoff button */
SP_ProgramMenuButton(SetRequiredFields,'signoff');
/* This function call is used to program onclick event of save button when Form is in checked out state*/
SP_ProgramMenuButton(EnableAllFields,'save');
/* This function call will set size of Attachemt and Links list fields */
SetSize();
/* This function call will retain height width of all text-areas */
SP_RetainHeightWidth();
/*This function call will expnad signature fields to show all signatures*/
SP_AdjustSignFieldSize();
/*This function call will set T1 Number of Records*/
SetNumOfRecords();
/*This function call will set state of fields in Related Records section*/
SP_SetRelatedRecords("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.SP_CFG_Complaint_Adv_Source","txtOther","ViewSource");
TaskTableFunctionality("btnAddComplaintTask","Complaint_Task_Count","hlpVisibleTasks","Complaint_Task_","Complaint_Tasks","Maintain State",10,"taskHeading");
CalcRiskScore();
EnableDidisableEMDRButton();
ManageInvestigateComplaint();
SetDynamicRequiredLabel();
ConfigureReportingTabs()
// Set Agent Name bug 43797
SetAgentName();
} catch(e){}
EnableDisableExtensionFields();
RefreshFieldProperties();
SetCurrentStep();
// Add/Remove Classes on buttons. It should be called at the end of StartupScript function
try{SP_ManipulateButtonClasses();}catch(e){};
}
/*STARTUPSCRIPT END*/
function setUpPrintingAndPublishing() {
window.onbeforeprint = function() {
$('textarea').each(function() {
var $this = $(this);
var text = ($this.val() === '')?'<br />':$this.val().replace(/\n/gi,'<br />');
var div = $('<div></div>')
.html(text)
.addClass('print-div');
if($this.hasClass('signatureField')) {
div
.css('border',0)
.addClass('signatureField');
}
$this
.addClass('print-hide')
.after(div);
});
}
window.onafterprint = function() {
$('.print-div').remove();
$('textarea.print-hide').removeClass('print-hide');
}
}
/*REFRESH FIELD PROPERTIES START*/
function RefreshFieldProperties(obj,tabName)
{
// This check make sure that function is either called from the Field events or from startup.
if(obj != null && tabName != null)
{
switch(decisionVariable)
{
case 1:
case "editform":
switch(tabName)
{
case "T1":
SetT1FieldProperties(obj);
break;
case 'T2':
SetT2FieldProperties(obj);
break;
case 'T3':
SetT3FieldProperties(obj);
break;
}
if(decisionVariable != "editform")
break;
case 3:
case "editform":
if(tabName == "T3")
{
SetT3FieldProperties(obj);
}
else if(tabName == "T4")
{
if(arguments[2])
SetT4FieldProperties(obj,arguments[2]);
else
SetT4FieldProperties(obj);
}
if(decisionVariable != "editform")
break;
case 4:
case "editform":
if(tabName == "T5")
{
SetT5FieldProperties(obj);
}
break;
}
SetDynamicRequiredLabel();
}
else
{
switch(decisionVariable)
{
case 1:
case "editform":
SetT2FieldProperties();
SetT3FieldProperties();
if(decisionVariable != "editform")
break;
case 3:
case "editform":
SetT3FieldProperties();
SetT4FieldProperties();
if(decisionVariable == 3)
{
DisableTabThreeFieldsOnStep3();
}
if(decisionVariable != "editform")
break;
case 4:
case "editform":
SetT5FieldProperties();
if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.route.esig.sigstatus.step4")) == "")
{
RearrangeTasks("hlpVisibleTasks","Complaint_Task_Count","Complaint_Task_");
TaskTableFunctionality("btnAddComplaintTask","Complaint_Task_Count","hlpVisibleTasks","Complaint_Task_","Complaint_Tasks","Maintain State",10,"taskHeading");
}
break;
}
}
switch(decisionVariable)
{
case 3:
case "editform":
break;
default:
document.getElementById("btnAddComplaintTask").disabled = true;
}
}
/*REFRESH FIELD PROPERTIES END*/
function SetT1FieldProperties(obj)
{
if(obj != null)
{
if(obj.name == "mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.SP_CFG_Complaint_Adv_Source")
{
SP_SetRelatedRecords("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.SP_CFG_Complaint_Adv_Source","txtOther","ViewSource");
}
}
}
function SetT2FieldProperties(obj)
{
if(obj != null)
{
switch(obj.name)
{
case "txtComplaintTitle":
SP_SetTaskTitle("txtComplaintTitle");
break;
case "chbHasCustomerId":
MCDataConfig(obj);
ShowUpdateButtonForCustomer();
break;
case "chbUpdateRecord":
EnableDatasetFields(obj);
ShowUpdateButtonForCustomer();
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers":
uploadCustomerMCData();
break;
case "cmbCountry":
hideCountrySelection();
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country":
showCountrySelection();
break;
case "cmbState":
hideStateSelection();
updateState();
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state":
showStateSelection();
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.update.Customers":
UpdateMCData();
SP_EnablePageFields(mcEditablePages);
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number":
EnableDisbaleUpdateButton(); //bug 34608
CheckPhone(obj);
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.postal code":
CheckZipCode(obj);
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company":
EnableDisbaleUpdateButton(); //bug 34608
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Products":
uploadProductMCData();
break;
case "chbUpdateProductRecord":
EnableProductDatasetFields(obj);
showUpdateButtonForProduct();
break;
case "mastercontrol.dataset.update.Products":
UpdateProductMCData();
SP_EnablePageFields(mcEditablePages);
break;
case "chbReportedMalfunction":
ManageReportedMalfunction();
break;
case "chbPRInitiated":
ManageProductRecoveryInitiated();
break;
case "txtAwarenessDate_date":
SP_ContinueAutoSave(true);
setMDRFilingDate();
if(sFormStatus == "editform" )
{
CalculateFilingDueDate("EUROPE");
CalculateFilingDueDate("CANADA");
}
break;
case "txtEventDate_date":
SP_ContinueAutoSave(true);
break;
}
}
else
{
SP_SetTaskCreator("txtCreatorName");
SP_SetTaskTitle("txtComplaintTitle");
CopyKeywords();
MapExtensionRequestData();
ManageHasCustomerId();
MCDataConfig();
ManageReportedMalfunction();
ManageProductRecoveryInitiated();
}
}
function SetT3FieldProperties(obj)
{
if(obj != null)
{
switch(obj.name)
{
case "chbHDOccured":
ManageSectionAQuestions();
setMDRRequired();
setMDRFilingDate();
break;
case "chbHIOccured":
ManageSectionBQuestions();
setMDRRequired();
setMDRFilingDate();
break;
case "chbHMOccured":
ManageSectionCQuestions();
setMDRRequired();
setMDRFilingDate();
break;
case "chbQA1":
case "chbQA2":
case "chbQA3":
case "chbQA4":
case "chbQA5":
case "chbQB1":
case "chbQB2":
case "chbQB3":
case "chbQB4":
case "chbQB5":
case "chbQC1":
case "chbQC2":
case "chbQC3":
case "chbQC4":
case "chbQC5":
setMDRRequired();
setMDRFilingDate();
break;
case "chbMDRnecessitate":
setMDRFilingDate();
break;
case "btnLauncheMDR":
CopyKeywords(); //Bug 31946; 30-Jun-2011
LaunchEMDR();
break;
case "rbHasEventOccured":
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceQListA",obj.name);
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbDeviceSuspected":
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceQListB",obj.name);
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbOutComes":
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceQListC",obj.name);
ManageViglanceCheckList('VQC2Subs',"rbVQC2");
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbVQC2":
ManageViglanceCheckList('VQC2Subs',"rbVQC2");
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbVQA1":
case "rbVQA2":
case "rbVQA3":
case "rbVQA4":
case "rbVQA5":
case "rbVQA6":
case "rbVQA7":
case "rbVQB1":
case "rbVQB2":
case "rbVQB3":
case "rbVQB4":
case "rbVQC1":
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbIncidentOccur":
case "rbDeficency":
case "rbEventCaused":
case "rbServiceLife":
case "rbProtection":
case "rbExpectedSideEffects":
case "rbNegligible":
EnableDisableVigilanceFields();
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbTimeFrame":
CalculateFilingDueDate("EUROPE");
break;
case "rbDeviceContributed":
ManageViglanceCheckList('VigilanceCQListB',"rbDeviceContributed");
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbIncOutComes":
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceCQListC",obj.name);
ManageViglanceCheckList('VCQC2SubOptions',"rbseriousDet");
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbseriousDet":
ManageViglanceCheckList('VCQC2SubOptions',"rbseriousDet");
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbIncidentOccured":
case "rbPatientDeath":
case "rbPotential":
SetDynamicRequiredLabel();
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbForeignIncidents":
case "rbDeficiencies":
case "rbIncidentCause":
case "rbMalfunction":
case "rbAbnormal":
case "rbIncOccuring":
SetDynamicRequiredLabel();
EnableDisableVigilanceFields();
SetReportRequired();
break;
case "rbVCTimeFrame":
CalculateFilingDueDate("CANADA");
break;
}
}
else
{
ManageSectionAQuestions();
ManageSectionBQuestions();
ManageSectionCQuestions();
if(stepId == 1)
{
setChecked("chbMDRRequired",1,true);
if(!getChecked("chbMDRnecessitate",0) && !getChecked("chbMDRnecessitate",1))
setChecked("chbMDRnecessitate",1,true);
document.getElementById("btnLauncheMDR").disabled = true;
// As per bug 43947
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceCQListC","rbIncOutComes");
ManageViglanceCheckList('VCQC2SubOptions',"rbseriousDet");
ManageViglanceCheckList('VigilanceCQListB',"rbDeviceContributed");
}
setMDRRequired();
//setMDRFilingDate();
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceQListA","rbHasEventOccured");
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceQListB","rbDeviceSuspected");
ManageVigilanceQuestions("VigilanceQListC","rbOutComes");
SetReportRequired();
ManageViglanceCheckList('VQC2Subs',"rbVQC2");
EnableDisableVigilanceFields();
}
}
function SetT4FieldProperties(obj) {
if(obj != null) {
for(var i = 1; i < 11; ++i) {
if (obj.name === "btnLaunchCIT" + i) {
LaunchActionItem('txtCITAINo' + i, i);
break;
}
else if (obj.name === "txtCITDateDue" + i + "_date") {
SetDueDate('txtCITDateDue', 'txtCIDueDate_date');
break;
}
else if (obj.name === "txtCITDateComplete" + i + "_date") {
SetDueDate('txtCITDateComplete', 'txtCIDateComplete_date');
break;
}
else if(obj.name === "btnRemoveCIT" + i) {
TaskTableFunctionality("btnAddComplaintTask", "Complaint_Task_Count", "hlpVisibleTasks", "Complaint_Task_", "Complaint_Tasks", "Remove Task", 10, "taskHeading", i);
SetDueDate('txtCITDateComplete', 'txtCIDateComplete_date');
SetDueDate('txtCITDateDue', 'txtCIDueDate_date');
DisableInvtigateComplaint();
break;
}
}
switch (obj.name) {
case "cmbType":
ManageComplaintInvestigationType("TypeSelectionChanged");
break;
case "cmbSubType":
ManageComplaintInvestigationSubType("SubTypeSelectionChanged");
break;
case "chbInvestigateComplaint":
ManageInvestigateComplaint("ShowTask");
ManageJustificationRequired();
break;
case "btnAddComplaintTask":
TaskTableFunctionality("btnAddComplaintTask", "Complaint_Task_Count", "hlpVisibleTasks", "Complaint_Task_", "Complaint_Tasks", "Add Task", 10, "taskHeading", "ActionItemBlock");
DisableInvtigateComplaint();
SetDynamicRequiredLabel();
break;
case "cmbFrequency":
case "cmbImpact":
CalcRiskScore();
break;
case "btnLaunchCAPA":
CopyKeywords("CAPA");
checkRiskScore();
break;
case "lbDeptsInvolved":
SP_ToggleVisibility("lbDeptsInvolved", "hlpDeptsInvolved_exclude", arguments[1], "EditShadow");
break;
case "hlpDeptsInvolved_exclude":
SP_ShowAllOptions("lbDeptsInvolved","hlpDeptsInvolved_exclude","EditShadow");
break;
}
}
else {
DisableInvtigateComplaint();
ManageComplaintInvestigationType();
ManageComplaintInvestigationSubType();
ManageInvestigateComplaint();
ManageJustificationRequired();
RearrangeTasks("hlpVisibleTasks", "Complaint_Task_Count", "Complaint_Task_");
TaskTableFunctionality("btnAddComplaintTask", "Complaint_Task_Count", "hlpVisibleTasks", "Complaint_Task_", "Complaint_Tasks", "Maintain State", 10, "taskHeading");
EnableDisableTasks();
DisableFieldsAfterLaunch("txtCAPARef", "cmbFrequency", "cmbImpact");
SP_ToggleVisibility("lbDeptsInvolved", "hlpDeptsInvolved_exclude");
}
}

function ManageCAPATypeSelection() {

SP_AddClass(document.getElementById('ViewIR'),'hide');
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById('ViewCAPA'),'hide');
} else if (CAPATYPE == 1 || CAPATYPE == 2) {
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById('LaunchCAPA'),'hide');
}
}
function ManageEMDRTypeSelection() {
if (EMDRTYPE == 0) {
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById('LaunchEMDR'),'hide');
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById('ViewEMDR'),'hide');
} else if (EMDRTYPE == 1) {
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById('LaunchEMDR'),'hide');
}
}
function ConfigureReportingTabs()
{
switch(decisionVariable)
{
case 1:
case 3:
case "editform":
SP_EnableAllFields("MDRTAB",REPORTEMDR);
SP_EnableAllFields("VIGILANCETAB_EU",REPORTEUROPE);
SP_EnableAllFields("VIGILANCETAB_CAN",REPORTCANADA);
SP_ShowHideCalendar("txtVCDateFiled_date");
SP_ShowHideCalendar("txtDateField_date");
SP_PerformAction("chbMDRRequired,rbReportingRequired,rbCanReportingRequired","disabled",true);
break;
}
}
function ManageHasCustomerId()
{
var oHasCustomerId = document.getElementsByName("chbHasCustomerId");
if(oHasCustomerId[0].checked == false && oHasCustomerId[1].checked == false)//Bug 26490, Date 24-Mar-2010
{
oHasCustomerId[1].checked = true;
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers").disabled = true;
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers"),"DisabledFormat");
}
}
function ManageReportedMalfunction()
{
if (SP_GetRGValue("chbReportedMalfunction") == "Yes")
{
SP_PerformAction("chbPRInitiated","disabled", false);
}
else
{
SP_PerformAction("chbPRInitiated","disabled empty", true);
SP_PerformAction("txtRUnrecoverable,txtRTNumber","disabled empty",true);
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("txtRUnrecoverable"),"DisabledFormat");
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("txtRTNumber"),"DisabledFormat");
}
}
function ManageProductRecoveryInitiated()
{
if (SP_GetRGValue("chbPRInitiated") == "Yes")
{
SP_PerformAction("txtRTNumber","disabled", false);
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("txtRTNumber"),"DisabledFormat");
SP_PerformAction("txtRUnrecoverable","disabled empty", true);
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("txtRUnrecoverable"),"DisabledFormat");
}
else if (SP_GetRGValue("chbPRInitiated") == "No")
{
SP_PerformAction("txtRUnrecoverable","disabled", false);
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("txtRUnrecoverable"),"DisabledFormat");
SP_PerformAction("txtRTNumber","disabled empty", true);
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("txtRTNumber"),"DisabledFormat");
}
else
{
SP_PerformAction("txtRUnrecoverable,txtRTNumber","disabled", true);
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("txtRUnrecoverable"),"DisabledFormat");
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("txtRTNumber"),"DisabledFormat");
}
}
function EnableDisbaleUpdateButton()
{
if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number").value) != "" && SP_Trim(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company").value) != "" && document.getElementById("chbUpdateRecord").checked == true)
{
SP_RemoveClass(updateButton,'hide');
}
else
{
SP_AddClass(updateButton,'hide');
}
}

function ManageComplaintInvestigationType()
{
var subTypeDropDown = document.getElementById("cmbSubType");
var count;
var subTypelength = subTypeDropDown.options.length;
if(arguments[0] == "TypeSelectionChanged")
{
if(document.getElementById("cmbType").value == "Other")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").disabled = false;
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").value = "";
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("N/A","N/A"));
subTypeDropDown.value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").value = "N/A";
}
else if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("cmbType").value) == "")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("N/A","N/A"));
subTypeDropDown.value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.disabled = true;
}
else if(document.getElementById("cmbType").value == "Product Defect")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.length = 0;
subTypeDropDown.disabled = false;
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option(" "," "));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Labeling","Labeling"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Packaging","Packaging"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Patient Information Leaflet (PIL)","Patient Information Leaflet (PIL)"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Product","Product"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Other","Other"));
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").value = "N/A";
}
else if(document.getElementById("cmbType").value == "Customer Service")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.length = 0;
subTypeDropDown.disabled = false;
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option(" "," "));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Billing Problem","Billing Problem"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Damaged Shipment","Damaged Shipment"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("General Inquiry/Suggestion","General Inquiry/Suggestion"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Incorrect Shipment","Incorrect Shipment"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Late/Lost Shipment","Late/Lost Shipment"));
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("Other","Other"));
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").value = "N/A";
}
}
else if(arguments[0] != "SubTypeSelectionChanged" && stepNumber != 0)
{ // when page loads and referesh property calls
if(document.getElementById("cmbType").value == "Other")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").disabled = false;
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("N/A","N/A"));
subTypeDropDown.value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.disabled = true;
}
else if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("cmbType").value) == "")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.options.add(new Option("N/A","N/A"));
subTypeDropDown.value = "N/A";
subTypeDropDown.disabled = true;
}
else
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherType").value = "N/A";
if(document.getElementById("cmbType").value == "Product Defect")
{
if(subTypeDropDown.length > 7)
{
subTypeDropDown.remove (1);
subTypeDropDown.remove (5);
subTypeDropDown.remove (5);
subTypeDropDown.remove (5);
subTypeDropDown.remove (5);
}
}
else if(document.getElementById("cmbType").value == "Customer Service")
{
if(subTypeDropDown.length > 7)
{
subTypeDropDown.remove (1);
subTypeDropDown.remove (1);
subTypeDropDown.remove (1);
subTypeDropDown.remove (1);
subTypeDropDown.remove (1);
}
}
subTypeDropDown.disabled = false;
}
}
var arr = ["cmbType","txtOtherType","cmbSubType","txtOtherSubType"];
for(i=0; i<arr.length; i++)
{
var obj = document.getElementById(arr[i]);
if(obj.disabled)
{
SP_AddClass(obj,"DisabledFormat");
SP_RemoveClass(obj,"EditShadow");
}
else
{
SP_RemoveClass(obj,"DisabledFormat");
SP_AddClass(obj,"EditShadow");
}
}
}

{
if(arguments[0] == "SubTypeSelectionChanged")
{
if(document.getElementById("cmbSubType").value == "Other")

document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").disabled = false;
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").value = "";
}
else if(document.getElementById("cmbSubType").value != "Other")
{

document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").value = "N/A";
}
}
else
{
if(document.getElementById("cmbSubType").value == "Other")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").disabled = false;
}
else if(document.getElementById("cmbSubType").value != "Other")
{
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").disabled = true;
document.getElementById("txtOtherSubType").value = "N/A";
}
}
var arr = ["cmbType","txtOtherType","cmbSubType","txtOtherSubType"];
for(i=0; i<arr.length; i++)
{
var obj = document.getElementById(arr[i]);
if(obj.disabled)
{
SP_AddClass(obj,"DisabledFormat");
SP_RemoveClass(obj,"EditShadow");
}
else
{
SP_RemoveClass(obj,"DisabledFormat");
SP_AddClass(obj,"EditShadow");
}
}
}

TaskTableFunctionality("btnAddComplaintTask","Complaint_Task_Count","hlpVisibleTasks","Complaint_Task_","Complaint_Tasks","Maintain State",10,"taskHeading");
}

else
{

{

document.getElementById("hlpVisibleTasks").value = "";
TaskTableFunctionality("btnAddComplaintTask","Complaint_Task_Count","hlpVisibleTasks","Complaint_Task_","Complaint_Tasks","Maintain State",10,"taskHeading");
}
}

function DisableInvtigateComplaint()
{//This Function will disable Investigate Complaint Radio button as soon as on Action Item Task is added
if(document.getElementById("Complaint_Task_Count").value*1 > 0)
{
SP_PerformAction("chbInvestigateComplaint","disabled",true);
}
else
{
SP_PerformAction("chbInvestigateComplaint","disabled",false);
}
}
function PutLaunchedFormNumber()
{
var sLaunchedForm = SP_Trim(document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedForm").value);
var sRefField = SP_Trim(document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedFormRefField").value);
if(sLaunchedForm != "" && sRefField != "")
{
switch(sLaunchedForm)
{
case "Action Item":
SP_PutLaunchedRef("mastercontrol.links.Action Item",SP_Trim(document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedFormRefField").value));
RearrangeTasks("hlpVisibleTasks","Complaint_Task_Count","Complaint_Task_");
EnableDisableTasks();
break;
case "CAPA":
SP_PutLaunchedRef('mastercontrol.links.CAPA',sRefField);
document.getElementById("InitiateCAPA").value = "CAPA";
break;
case "Issue Review Adv":
SP_PutLaunchedRef("mastercontrol.links.Issue Review Adv",sRefField);
document.getElementById("InitiateCAPA").value = "Issue Review Launched";
break;
case "eMDR":
if(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.links.eMDR").length>0)
{
document.getElementById("InitiateeMDR").value = "eMDR Launched";
SP_PutLaunchedRef("mastercontrol.links.eMDR",sRefField);
}
else
{
document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedForm").value = "";
document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedFormRefField").value = "";
}
break;
}
document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedForm").value = "";
document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedFormRefField").value = "";
}
}

InitiateQuestions();
ManageSectionAQuestions();
ManageSectionBQuestions();
ManageSectionCQuestions();
}

{
document.getElementById("btnLauncheMDR").disabled = true;
}
else
{
document.getElementById("btnLauncheMDR").disabled = false;
}
}
else
{
document.getElementById("btnLauncheMDR").disabled = true;
}
}
}

{

setChecked("chbJustificationRequired",1,false);

{

setChecked("chbJustificationRequired",1,true);
}
}
function ManageInvestigationOutCome()
{ /*This function will Enable Disable the text field "Other Investigation Outcome"
on the basis of value selected in investigation outcome combo box*/

{
document.getElementById("txtOtherInvestigationOutcome").disabled = false;

}
else
{

document.getElementById("txtOtherInvestigationOutcome").value = "";

SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("txtOtherInvestigationOutcome"),"DisabledFormat");
}
}
function InitiateQuestions()
{
//This function will initiate the sub question in MDR/Adverse Event Evaluation section in MDR(T3)
var questionText;
document.getElementById("QA1").innerHTML = A1;
document.getElementById("QA2").innerHTML = A2;
document.getElementById("QA3").innerHTML = A3;
document.getElementById("QA4").innerHTML = A4;
document.getElementById("QA5").innerHTML = A5;
document.getElementById("QB1").innerHTML = B1;
document.getElementById("QB2").innerHTML = B2;
document.getElementById("QB3").innerHTML = B3;
document.getElementById("QB4").innerHTML = B4;
document.getElementById("QB5").innerHTML = B5;
document.getElementById("QC1").innerHTML = C1;
document.getElementById("QC2").innerHTML = C2;
document.getElementById("QC3").innerHTML = C3;
document.getElementById("QC4").innerHTML = C4;
document.getElementById("QC5").innerHTML = C5;
for(i=1; i<=5; i++)
{
questionText = arrayQuestionsA[i-1];
if(questionText == "N/A")
{
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("RA"+i),'hide');
}
else
{
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("RA"+i),'hide');
}
questionText = arrayQuestionsB[i-1];
if(questionText == "N/A")
{
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("RB"+i),'hide');
}
else
{
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("RB"+i),'hide');
}
questionText = arrayQuestionsC[i-1];
if(questionText == "N/A")
{
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("RC"+i),'hide');
}
else
{
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("RC"+i),'hide');
}
}
}
function setMDRRequired()
{
/*This function will make eMDR launch required if any of the sub question in
MDR/Adverse Event Evaluation section is answered as yes*/
var checked = false;
var QuestionA;
var QuestionB;
var QuestionC;
var oRadioList = document.getElementsByName("chbMDRnecessitate");
for(j=1; j<= 5; j++)
{
QuestionA = document.getElementById("chbQA"+j).checked;
QuestionB = document.getElementById("chbQB"+j).checked;
QuestionC = document.getElementById("chbQC"+j).checked;
if(QuestionA == true || QuestionB == true || QuestionC == true)
{
checked = true;
break;
}
}
if(checked == true)
{
setChecked("chbMDRRequired",0,true);
oRadioList[0].disabled = false;
oRadioList[1].disabled = false;
}
else
{
setChecked("chbMDRRequired",1,true);
setChecked("chbMDRnecessitate",1,true);
oRadioList[0].disabled = true;
oRadioList[1].disabled = true;
}
EnableDidisableEMDRButton();
SP_ManipulateButtonClasses();
}
function setMDRFilingDate()
{
/*This wfunction will populate dat in MDR Filing Due Date*/
var days = "";
if(getChecked("chbMDRRequired",0) == true && !getChecked("chbMDRnecessitate",0))
{
SP_PerformAction("txtFillingDueDate_date","disabled",false);
days = 30;
}
else if(getChecked("chbMDRRequired",0) == true && getChecked("chbMDRnecessitate",0) == true)
{
SP_PerformAction("txtFillingDueDate_date","disabled",false);
days = 5;
}
else if(getChecked("chbMDRRequired",1) == true)//Added under 34239
{
SP_PerformAction("txtFillingDueDate_date","disabled empty",true);
}
if(days != "")
{
if(SP_Trim($("#txtAwarenessDate_date").val()) != "")
{
var awarenessDate = new Date($("#txtAwarenessDate_date").datepicker('getDate'));
var date = new Date(awarenessDate.getTime()+days*24*60*60*1000);
MC.Utils.Date.Parse({
date: date.getFullYear()+" "+(date.getMonth()+ 1)+" "+date.getDate(),
successCallback:function( result ){
document.getElementById("txtFillingDueDate_date").value = result.date;
}
});
}
}
SP_ShowHideCalendar("txtFillingDueDate_date");
}

}
}
//Improved under bug 31946; 30-Jun-2011
//fixed bug 25821; 5-Aug-2011
function CopyKeywords()
{
var issueNo = document.getElementById("txtComplaintNumber");
var formNo = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.form.number");
var dateCreated = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.form.created");
var CAPADateCreated = document.getElementById("txtComplaintDateCreated_date");
var whatWhereWhen = document.getElementById("txtWhatWhenWhere");
var What = document.getElementById("txtWhat").value;
var Where = document.getElementById("txtWhere").value;
var When = document.getElementById("txtWhen").value;
var Weight = document.getElementById("txtWeight").value;
var Who = document.getElementById("txtWho").value;
// MC data Customer Fields
document.getElementById("txtCompany").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company").value;
document.getElementById("txtPhoneNumber").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number").value;
document.getElementById("txtEmailAddress").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.contact email address").value;
document.getElementById("txtAddress").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.address").value;
document.getElementById("txtCity").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.city").value;
document.getElementById("txtPostalCode").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.postal code").value;
if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state").value) == "NY")
{document.getElementById("txtState").value = "New York";}
else
{document.getElementById("txtState").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state").value;}
document.getElementById("txtCountry").value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country").value;
issueNo.value = formNo.value;
CAPADateCreated.value = dateCreated.value;
if(arguments[0])
{
if(CAPATYPE == 1)
{
whatWhereWhen.value = "What:"+"\n"+ TruncateValue(What)+ "\n\n" +"Where:"+"\n"+ TruncateValue(Where)+ "\n\n" +"When:" + "\n"+ TruncateValue(When)+ "\n\n" +"Weight:" +"\n"+ TruncateValue(Weight)+ "\n\n" +"Who:" + "\n"+ TruncateValue(Who);
}
}
}
//fixed bug 25821; 5-Aug-2011
function TruncateValue()
{
if(arguments[0].length > 350)
{
return arguments[0].substring(0,350)+"...";
}
else
{
return arguments[0];
}
}

function showCountrySelection()
{

{

SP_AddClass(DisplayCountry,'hide');
}
}

SP_AddClass(SelectCountry,'hide');
SP_RemoveClass(DisplayCountry,'hide');
}
//fixing bug ref: 27857; 9-Jun-2010
function HoldSelectedState()
{
var subTypeDropDown = document.getElementById("cmbState");
if(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state").value != "")
{
DisplayedState = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state").value;
for (i=0;i<subTypeDropDown.length;i++)
{
if(subTypeDropDown.options[i].value == DisplayedState)
{
subTypeDropDown.options[i].selected = true;
}
}
}
}

//Dated: 02-Apr-2010; Bug ref: 26489
//Improved under bug 32426
function MapExtensionRequestData()
{
//Setting Source Title
var MapSourceTitle = document.getElementById("txtSourceTitle");
if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("txtComplaintTitle").value) == "")
{
MapSourceTitle.value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.form.number").value;
}
else
{
MapSourceTitle.value = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.form.title").value;
}
document.getElementById("hlpSource").value = "Complaint";
//Setting Extension Request Approvers to be passed
SP_MapERapprovers('mastercontrol.role.SP_COMP_ExtReqApprovers','hlpExtReqApprovers');
}
// Logic implemented related to Launch Extension Request
//Improved under bug 27133; 23-Apr-2010
function LaunchExtensionRequest()
{
SP_UnrequireFields();
if(stepId == 1)
{
MapExtensionRequestData();
}
SP_SelectRouteLaunched("Extension Request","mastercontrol.task.mapped.routes.ER");
RunExtReqCounter();
}
/**************FUNCTIONS ARE MEANT TO SET EXTENSION REQUEST COUNTER******************/
//Bug 27299; 27-Jul-2010
function RunExtReqCounter()
{
if(stepId.value != "")
{
var ERCounter = document.getElementById("ERCounter_num");
var isLaunching = SP_IsRouteSelected("Extension Request" , "mastercontrol.task.mapped.routes.ER");
if(isLaunching)
{
SP_EnablePageFields(mcEditablePages);
if(ERCounter.disabled)
{
ERCounter.disabled = false;
}
ERCounter.value = (ERCounter.value * 1) + 1;
}
}
}
//**********************************************************************************
// Logic implemented Related to enable/disable Extension Request Button
function EnableDisableExtensionFields()
{
var ERLinks = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.links.Extension Request");
var btnERLaunch = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.task.mapped.launch.ER");
var btnViewRequests = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.links.view.Extension Request");
var ERCounter = document.getElementById("ERCounter_num");
if(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.route.stepduedate").value != "")
{
btnERLaunch.disabled = false;
}
else
{
btnERLaunch.disabled = true;
}
if(ERCounter.value > 0)
{
btnViewRequests.disabled = false;
}
else
{
btnViewRequests.disabled = true;
}
}

// This method upload the MC data for Customer Information
//
function uploadCustomerMCData()
{
var customerId = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers").value;
if( SP_Trim(customerId) != "")
{
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.show.Customers").click();
}
else
{
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company").value = "";
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number").value = "";
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.contact email address").value = "";
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.address").value = "";
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.city").value = "";
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state").value = "";
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.postal code").value = "";
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country").value = "";
}
}

//Redesigned to fix bug 27857; 9-Jun-2010
function updateCountry()
{
var DisplayCountry = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country");
var SelectionCountry = document.getElementById("cmbCountry");
var holdPrevValue = DisplayCountry.value;
var CountryState = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state");
var PCode = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.postal code");
var phNum = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number");
if(DisplayCountry.value != SelectionCountry.value)
{
DisplayCountry.value = SelectionCountry.value;
if(SP_Trim(CountryState.value)!="" || SP_Trim(PCode.value)!="" || SP_Trim(phNum.value) !="")
{
var returnvalue = confirm("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L20#");
if(returnvalue)
{
CountryState.value = '';
PCode.value = '';
phNum.value = '';
DisplayCountry.focus();
}
else
{
DisplayCountry.value = holdPrevValue;
SelectionCountry.value = holdPrevValue;
}
}
}
}
//Updated under 34240
function CheckZipCode(fZipCode )
{
//this.refreshCall=true;
fCountry = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country");
var zip = fZipCode.value.toString();
if( fCountry.value == "United States of America" && SP_Trim(zip)!="" )
{
postalCodeRegex = /^\d{5}(-\d{4})?$/;
var pattern = postalCodeRegex.test(zip);
if (!pattern)
{
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L9#");
fZipCode.value="";
fZipCode.focus();
}
}
else if( fCountry.value == "Canada" && SP_Trim(zip)!="" )
{
postalCodeRegex = /^[A-Za-z0-9]{3}[ ][A-Za-z0-9]{3}$/;
var pattern = postalCodeRegex.test(zip);
if (!pattern)
{
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L10#");
fZipCode.value="";
fZipCode.focus();
}
else
{
//alert(false);
}
}
else if( fCountry.value == "Mexico" && SP_Trim(zip)!="" )
{
postalCodeRegex = /^[A-Za-z0-9]{5}[-][A-Za-z0-9]{4}$/;
var pattern = postalCodeRegex.test(zip);
if (!pattern)
{
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L11#");
fZipCode.value="";
fZipCode.focus();
}
}
SP_ContinueAutoSave(false);
}
function CheckPhone(phonenumber)
{
fCountry = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country");
var phone = phonenumber.value.toString();
if( fCountry.value == "United States of America" && SP_Trim(phone)!="" )
{
postalCodeRegex = /^[A-Za-z0-9]{3}[-][A-Za-z0-9]{3}[-][A-Za-z0-9]{4}$/;
var pattern = postalCodeRegex.test(phone);
if (!pattern)
{
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L12#");
phonenumber.value="";
phonenumber.focus();
}
}
else if( fCountry.value == "Canada" && SP_Trim(phone)!="" )
{
postalCodeRegex = /^[A-Za-z0-9]{3}[-][A-Za-z0-9]{3}[-][A-Za-z0-9]{4}$/;
var pattern = postalCodeRegex.test(phone);
if (!pattern)
{
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L13#");
phonenumber.value="";
phonenumber.focus();
}
}
else if( fCountry.value == "Mexico" && SP_Trim(phone)!="" )
{
postalCodeRegex = /^\d\d[- ]?\d\d\d\d\d\d\d\d$/;
var pattern = postalCodeRegex.test(phone);
if (!pattern)
{
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L14#");
phonenumber.value="";
phonenumber.focus();
}
}
SP_ContinueAutoSave(false);
}
function updateState()
{
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state").value = document.getElementById("cmbState").value;
}
//fixed bug 32342; Dated: 19-Aug-2011
//updated under 34601
function MCDataConfig()
{
var fields = "mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number,"+
"mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.contact email address,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.address,"+
"mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.city,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state,"+
"mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.postal code,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country";
if(SP_GetRGValue("chbHasCustomerId") == "Yes")
{
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("editibleCID"),'hide');
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("readonlyCID"),'hide');
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers,chbUpdateRecord","disabled",false);
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers"),"DisabledFormat");
if(arguments[0])
SP_PerformAction(fields,"empty",true);
SP_PerformAction(fields,"disabled",true);
}
else
{
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("editibleCID"),'hide');
SP_RemoveClass(document.getElementById("readonlyCID"),'hide');
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers,chbUpdateRecord","disabled empty",true);
SP_AddClass(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers"),"DisabledFormat");
if(arguments[0])
SP_PerformAction(fields,"empty",true);
SP_PerformAction(fields,"disabled",false);
}
var arr = fields.split(",");
for(i=0; i<arr.length; i++)
{
var obj = document.getElementById(arr[i]);
if(obj.disabled)
{
SP_AddClass(obj,"DisabledFormat");
}
else
{
SP_RemoveClass(obj,"DisabledFormat");
}
}
}
// updated under Bug 34601
function EnableDatasetFields(selectedCheckboxOption)
{
if(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers").value != "")
{
var fields = "mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number,"+
"mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.contact email address,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.address,"+
"mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.city,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.state,"+
"mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.postal code,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.country";
if(selectedCheckboxOption.checked == true)
{
SP_RemoveClass(updateButton,'hide');
SP_RemoveClass(editibleCID,'hide');
SP_AddClass(readonlyCID,'hide');
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers","disabled",true);
SP_PerformAction(fields,"disabled",false);
SP_PerformAction(fields,"readonly",false);
}
else
{
SP_AddClass(updateButton,'hide');
SP_RemoveClass(editibleCID,'hide');
SP_AddClass(readonlyCID,'hide');
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers","disabled",false);
SP_PerformAction(fields,"readonly",true);
}
}
else
{
selectedCheckboxOption.checked = false;
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L15#");
}
}
function EnableProductDatasetFields(selectedCheckboxOption)
{
if(document.getElementById("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Products").value != "")
{
if(selectedCheckboxOption.checked == true)
{
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Products","disabled", true);
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.Products.product description","readonly", false);
}
else
{
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Products","disabled", false);
SP_PerformAction("mastercontrol.dataset.Products.product description","readonly", true);
}
}
else
{
alert("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L16#");
document.getElementById("chbUpdateProductRecord").checked = false;
}
}
// This function makes the field required
//Modified under bug 32342; Date: 19-Aug-2011
function SetRequiredFields()
{
SP_UnrequireFields();
switch(decisionVariable)
{
case 1:
case "editform":
mcRequireToggle("txtComplaintTitle,txtName,txtEventDate_date,txtAwarenessDate_date",true);
if(SP_GetRGValue("chbHasCustomerId") == "Yes")
{
mcRequireToggle("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers", true);
mcRequireToggle("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number", false);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.Customers", false);
mcRequireToggle("mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.company,mastercontrol.dataset.Customers.phone number", true);
}
if (SP_GetRGValue("chbReportedMalfunction") == "Yes")
{
mcRequireToggle('chbPRInitiated',true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle('chbPRInitiated',false);
}
if (SP_GetRGValue("chbPRInitiated") == "Yes")
{
mcRequireToggle('txtRUnrecoverable',false);
mcRequireToggle('txtRTNumber',true);
}
else if (SP_GetRGValue("chbPRInitiated") == "No")
{
mcRequireToggle('txtRTNumber',false);
mcRequireToggle('txtRUnrecoverable',true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle('txtRUnrecoverable',false);
mcRequireToggle('txtRTNumber',false);
}
if(REPORTEUROPE == "true")
{
var exclusionFields = ["rbIncidentOccur","rbDeficency","rbEventCaused","rbServiceLife","rbProtection","rbExpectedSideEffects","rbNegligible"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(SP_GetRGValue(exclusionFields[i]) == "Yes")
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
mcRequireToggle('txtJustification',exclusionFlag);
}
if(REPORTCANADA == "true")
{
var flag = SP_GetRGValue("rbIncidentOccured") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbDeviceContributed") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbIncOutComes") == "Yes";
mcRequireToggle('rbPatientDeath,rbseriousDet,rbPotential',flag);
var exclusionFields = ["rbForeignIncidents","rbDeficiencies","rbIncidentCause","rbMalfunction","rbAbnormal","rbIncOccuring"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(SP_GetRGValue(exclusionFields[i]) == "Yes")
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
mcRequireToggle('txtVCJustification',exclusionFlag);
}
if(decisionVariable != "editform")
break;
case 3:
case "editform":
if(REPORTEUROPE == "true")
{
var exclusionFields = ["rbIncidentOccur","rbDeficency","rbEventCaused","rbServiceLife","rbProtection","rbExpectedSideEffects","rbNegligible"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(SP_GetRGValue(exclusionFields[i]) == "Yes")
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
if(GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListA") && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListB") && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListC") && !exclusionFlag)
{
mcRequireToggle("txtFiling_date,txtDateField_date,txtReportReference,rbTimeFrame",true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle("txtFiling_date,txtDateField_date,txtReportReference,rbTimeFrame",false);
}
}
if(REPORTCANADA == "true")
{
var exclusionFields = ["rbForeignIncidents","rbDeficiencies","rbIncidentCause","rbMalfunction","rbAbnormal","rbIncOccuring"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(SP_GetRGValue(exclusionFields[i]) == "Yes")
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
if(SP_GetRGValue("rbIncidentOccured") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbDeviceContributed") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbIncOutComes") == "Yes" && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceCQListC") && !exclusionFlag)
{
mcRequireToggle("txtVCReportReference,txtVCDateFiled_date,txtVCFilingDate_date,rbVCTimeFrame",true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle("txtVCReportReference,txtVCDateFiled_date,txtVCFilingDate_date,rbVCTimeFrame",false);
}
}
if(SP_GetRGValue("chbInvestigateComplaint") == "No" && (document.getElementById("txteMDRRef").value == "") && document.getElementById("txtCAPARef").value =="")
{
mcRequireToggle("mastercontrol.dataset.recordids.SP_CFG_Complaint_Adv_Justification,txtJustificationDetail,chbInvestigateComplaint",true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle("chbInvestigateComplaint",true);
}
if(SP_GetRGValue("chbMDRRequired") == "Yes" && EMDRTYPE == 1)
{
mcRequireToggle('InitiateeMDR',true);
}
else if (SP_GetRGValue('chbMDRRequired') == 'Yes' && EMDRTYPE == 0) {
mcRequireToggle('txteMDRRef',true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle('InitiateeMDR,txteMDRRef',false);
}
if(document.getElementById("txtFXI_num").value*1 >14 && CAPATYPE != 0)
{
mcRequireToggle('InitiateCAPA',true);
}
else if (document.getElementById("txtFXI_num").value*1 >14 && CAPATYPE == 0) {
mcRequireToggle('txtCAPARef',true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle('InitiateCAPA,txtCAPARef',false);
}
if(SP_GetRGValue("chbInvestigateComplaint") == "Yes")
{
mcRequireToggle("txtFindings",true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle("txtFindings",false);
}
var taskCounter = document.getElementById("Complaint_Task_Count").value*1;
if(taskCounter > 0)
{
var fields = "";
for(ic=1;ic<=taskCounter;ic++)
{
fields = fields+'txtCITDateComplete'+ic+"_date,";
}
mcRequireToggle(fields,true);
}
if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("txtCIDateComplete_date").value) != "")
{
mcRequireToggle("txtCompletionSummary",true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle("txtCompletionSummary",false);
}
// Rationale required on basis of CAPA Launch
if(SP_Trim(document.getElementById("txtCAPARef").value) == "")
{
mcRequireToggle("txtRationale",true);
}
else
{
mcRequireToggle("txtRationale",false);
}
break;
}
}

functionality of Complaint Investigation Complete field,

function SetTaskCompleteStatus(chbComplete, Datefield)
{
var oChb = document.getElementById(chbComplete);
var oTaskCounter = document.getElementById("Complaint_Task_Count").value;
var visibleTasks = document.getElementById("hlpVisibleTasks").value.split(",");
var cbName = "Complaint Investigation Complete";
var TaskCompDate = "";
var isCompDateExist = 0;
for(i=0; i<visibleTasks.length; i++)
{
if(SP_Trim(visibleTasks[i]) != "")
{
TaskCompDate = document.getElementById(Datefield+visibleTasks[i]+"_date").value;
if(SP_Trim(TaskCompDate)!="")
{
isCompDateExist++;
}
}
}
if(isCompDateExist != oTaskCounter)
{
if(arguments[2] == 'ShowAlert')
{
alert(" #mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L17# "+cbName+".");
oChb.checked = false;
}
else
{
oChb.checked = false;
}
}
}

function CalcRiskScore()
{
var x = document.getElementById("cmbFrequency").value;
var y = document.getElementById("cmbImpact").value;
var z = document.getElementById("txtFXI_num");
z.value = x * y;
if (z.value < 5)
{
z.className = "ScoreGreen";
}
else if (z.value > 4 && z.value < 15)
{
z.className = "ScoreYellow";
}
else if (z.value > 14)
{
z.className = "ScoreRed";
}
}
function getValue(radioGroupName)
{
var oRadioList = document.getElementsByName(radioGroupName);
for (i = 0; i < oRadioList.length; i++)
{
if (oRadioList[i].checked) return oRadioList[i].value;
}
}
function getChecked(radioGroupName,index)
{
var oRadioList = document.getElementsByName(radioGroupName);
return oRadioList[index].checked;
}
function setChecked(radioGroupName,index,state)
{
var oRadioList = document.getElementsByName(radioGroupName);
oRadioList[index].checked = state;
}

//improved to fix bug 27182; 26-Apr-2010
//updated under bug 30727
function LaunchActionItem(refField, n) {
var validDate = '',
aiDate = 'txtCITDateDue' + n + '_date',
dueDate = 'mastercontrol.route.stepduedate';
validDate = SP_CompareDates(aiDate, dueDate);
if (validDate === 1 || validDate === '') {
alert('#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L31#');
document.getElementById(dueDate).value = '';
return;
}
SP_UnrequireFields();
if (SetRequiredOnLaunch(n)) {
if (SP_SelectRouteLaunched('Action Item', 'mastercontrol.task.routes')) {
if (SP_IsRouteSelected('Action Item', 'mastercontrol.task.routes')) {
MapAIValues(n);
if (decisionVariable === 'editform') {
SP_EnableAllFields('Customer_Complaint', true);
}
else {
SP_EnablePageFields(mcEditablePages);
}
/* Bug 28859 Ends */
document.getElementById('txtDefaultTab').value = 4;
document.getElementById('hlpLaunchedForm').value = 'Action Item';
document.getElementById('hlpLaunchedFormRefField').value = refField;
document.getElementById('mastercontrol.task.launch').click();
}
}
}
}
function SetRequiredOnLaunch(n)
{
var flag = false;
var allreqfields;
var allreqLabels;
allrequiredfields = 'txtCIT'+n+',txtCITDateDue'+n+'_date,mastercontrol.role.SP_COMP_TaskOwners.CITOwner'+n;
allreqLabels = 'lblCIT'+n+',txtCITDateDue'+n+'_date,lblOwnerCIT'+n;
var tf1 = document.getElementById('txtCIT'+n).value;
var tf2 = document.getElementById('txtCITDateDue'+n+'_date').value;
var tf3 = document.getElementById('mastercontrol.role.SP_COMP_TaskOwners.CITOwner'+n).value;
mcRequireToggle(allrequiredfields,true);
SetTaskFieldsLabel(allrequiredfields,allreqLabels);
if(SP_Trim(tf1)!= "" && SP_Trim(tf2)!= "" && SP_Trim(tf3)!= "")
{
flag = true;
}
return flag;
}
/******
MapAIValues() function . Function copies the values to be transferred to AI form into a hidden field.
Script from AI form will parse values from the hidden field and put them in relevant fields.
***/
//IMPROVED under bug: 27800; Dated: 4-Jun-2010
//Modified under bug 32205; Dated 3-Aug-2011
function MapAIValues(n)
{
var f1 = document.getElementById("hlpAItitle");
var f2 = document.getElementById("hlpAItaskOwner");
var f3 = document.getElementById("hlpAItaskDue_date");
var f4 = document.getElementById("hlpSource");
var f5 = document.getElementById("hlpAITaskType")
var f6 = document.getElementById("hlpAItaskOwnerID")
var n=n*1;
f1.value = document.getElementById("txtCIT"+n).value;
var rollName = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.role.SP_COMP_TaskOwners.CITOwner"+n);
f2.value = rollName.options[rollName.selectedIndex].text;
f3.value = document.getElementById("txtCITDateDue"+n+"_date").value;
f4.value = "Customer Complaint";
f5.value = "Investigation Task";
f6.value = SP_GetUserID(rollName.value);
}
/*
* @author: jvanwagenen
* @param: {string} stepDueDate - ID for the step due date that the new task can't be later than
* @param: {string} targetActionDate - ID for the due date for the task that's going to be launched. Cannot be later than the stepDueDate.
* @param: {string} overallDueDate - ID for the overall due date which is the field that's automatically updated. Passed in so we can clear it out if there's an error with the dates
*/
function CompareWithApprovalDate(stepDueDate, targetActionDate, overallDueDate) {
if (SP_CompareDates(targetActionDate, stepDueDate) === 1) {
alert('#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L31#');
if (overallDueDate) {
document.getElementById(overallDueDate).value = '';
}
else {
document.getElementById(targetActionDate).value = '';
}
return false;
}
return true;
}
/*
* @author: jvanwagenen
* @param: {string} partialId - partial ID of an element (i.e. 'txtContnmntTaskDue')
* @param: {Number} fieldsCount - the number of elements to iterate over (if there are 5, pass 5)
*/
function getLatestDate(partialId, fieldsCount) {
var fieldID = "",
value = new Date(),
i = 1,
maxIndex = 1,
max = new Date(1970, 0, 1);
for(; i <= fieldsCount; ++i) {
fiedID = '#' + partialId + i + '_date';
if ($(fiedID).val() != '') {
value = $(fiedID).datepicker('getDate');
if (value > max) {
maxIndex = i;
max = value;
}
}
}
return {
index: maxIndex,
value: max
};
}
///////////////////// Bug ref #25877; Dated: 01-Mar-2010///////////////////
//Improved under bug 32426; Dated: 27-Sep-2011
function SetDueDate(duDt, targetField) {
var LatestDate = getLatestDate(duDt, 10),
dateString = '',
stepDueDate = 'mastercontrol.route.stepduedate';
if (LatestDate != '') {
dateString = LatestDate.value.getFullYear() + '-' + (LatestDate.value.getMonth() + 1) + '-' + LatestDate.value.getDate();
switch (targetField) {
case 'txtCIDueDate_date':
MC.Utils.Date.Parse({
date: dateString, //Your date string here
successCallback: function (result) {
document.getElementById('txtCIDueDate_date').value = result.date;
CompareWithApprovalDate(stepDueDate, duDt + LatestDate.index + '_date', targetField);
}
});
break;
case 'txtCIDateComplete_date':
MC.Utils.Date.Parse({
date: dateString, //Your date string here
successCallback: function (result) {
document.getElementById('txtCIDateComplete_date').value = result.date;
SetDynamicRequiredLabel();
}
});
break;
}
}
else {
document.getElementById(targetField).value = '';
SetDynamicRequiredLabel();
}
}
function checkRiskScore()
{
var x = document.getElementById("cmbFrequency").value;
var y = document.getElementById("cmbImpact").value;
if (x * y < 15)
{
var selection = window.confirm("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L21#");
if(selection)
{
LaunchCAPA();
}
}
else
{
LaunchCAPA();
}
}

// Mathod that will be called on CAPA launch click button
//updated under bug 30727
function LaunchCAPA()
{
var selectedCAPAForm;
document.getElementById("hlpSource").value = "Complaint";
if( CAPATYPE == 1)
{
selectedCAPAForm = "CAPA";
}
else if (CAPATYPE == 2)
{
selectedCAPAForm = "Issue Review Adv";
}
SP_UnrequireFields();
SP_SelectRouteLaunched(selectedCAPAForm,"mastercontrol.task.routes");
if(SP_IsRouteSelected(selectedCAPAForm,"mastercontrol.task.routes"))
{
if(decisionVariable == "editform")
SP_EnableAllFields("Customer_Complaint",true);
else
SP_EnablePageFields(mcEditablePages);
document.getElementById("txtDefaultTab").value = 4;
document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedForm").value = selectedCAPAForm;
document.getElementById("hlpLaunchedFormRefField").value = "txtCAPARef";
}
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.task.launch").click();
}

}

function DisplayViewLinksButtons()
{
if (EMDRTYPE == 0 && SP_FieldIsOnEditablePage('txteMDRRef',mcEditablePages)) {

}
else if (EMDRTYPE == 1) {
SP_SwapButtonAfterLaunch("txteMDRRef","LaunchEMDR","ViewEMDR","mastercontrol.links.view.eMDR");
}
if (CAPATYPE == 0 && SP_FieldIsOnEditablePage('txtCAPARef',mcEditablePages)){
SP_PerformAction('txtCAPARef','readonly',false);
}
else if(CAPATYPE == 2)
{
SP_SwapButtonAfterLaunch("txtCAPARef","LaunchCAPA","ViewIR","mastercontrol.links.view.Issue Review Adv");
}
else if(CAPATYPE == 1)
{
SP_SwapButtonAfterLaunch("txtCAPARef","LaunchCAPA","ViewCAPA","mastercontrol.links.view.CAPA");
}
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.links.view.Action Item").disabled = false;
}

function EnableDisableTasks()
{
var fName = "txtCITAINo";
var fieldsLst = new Array("txtCIT","mastercontrol.role.SP_COMP_TaskOwners.CITOwner","txtCITDateDue","btnLaunchCIT","btnRemoveCIT");
var TaskRef = "";
for(var i=1; i<=10; i++)
{
TaskRef = document.getElementById(fName+i).value;
if(SP_Trim(TaskRef)!="")
{
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[0]+i).disabled = true;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[1]+i).disabled = true;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[2]+i+"_date").disabled = true;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[3]+i).disabled = true;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[4]+i).disabled = true;
}
else
{
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[0]+i).disabled = false;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[1]+i).disabled = false;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[2]+i+"_date").disabled = false;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[3]+i).disabled = false;
document.getElementById(fieldsLst[4]+i).disabled = false;
}
SP_ShowHideCalendar(fieldsLst[2]+i+"_date");
}
}

// Code related to 33179 start
function TaskTableFunctionality()
{
var oAddTaskButton = document.getElementById(arguments[0]);
var oTaskCounter = document.getElementById(arguments[1]);
var oVisibleTasks = document.getElementById(arguments[2]);
var taskContainer = arguments[3];
var refSecContainer = arguments[4];
var action = SP_Trim(arguments[5]);
var totalTasks = arguments[6]*1;
var taskHeading = SP_Trim(arguments[7]);
switch(action)
{
case "Add Task":
if (++oTaskCounter.value<= totalTasks)
{
var index = FindLocation(oVisibleTasks.value,totalTasks);
var mainContainer = SP_Trim(arguments[8]);
SP_RemoveClass($("#"+taskContainer+index).get(0),'hide');
oVisibleTasks.value += index+",";
$.each(oVisibleTasks.value.split(","),function()
{
if(SP_Trim(this) != "")
{
$("#"+mainContainer).append($("#"+taskContainer+this));
}
});
}
break;
case "Remove Task":
if (oTaskCounter.value>0)
{
var flag = true;
var index = arguments[8]*1;
if(DoesTaskContainData(taskContainer+index))
{
var taskHeader = SP_Trim(document.getElementById(taskHeading+index).innerHTML);
var result = confirm("#mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L29# \'"+taskHeader+"\' #mastercontrol.translate.SP_TRANS_HCOMP.C_L30#");
if(!result)
{
flag = false;
}
}
if(flag == true)
{
RemoveDataFromTask(taskContainer+index);
SP_AddClass($("#"+taskContainer+index).get(0),'hide');
oVisibleTasks.value = oVisibleTasks.value.replace(index+",","");
--oTaskCounter.value;
if(oTaskCounter.value == 0)
{
oVisibleTasks.value = "";
}
}
}
break;
case "Maintain State":
for(m=1; m<=totalTasks; m++)
{
SP_AddClass($("#"+taskContainer+m).get(0),'hide');
}
$.each(oVisibleTasks.value.split(","),function()
{
if(SP_Trim(this) != "")
{
SP_RemoveClass($("#"+taskContainer+this).get(0),'hide');
}
});
break;
case "Reset Table":
for(r=1; r<=totalTasks; r++)
{
SP_AddClass($("#"+taskContainer+r).get(0),'hide');
$("#"+taskContainer+r+"").find("input:not(input[type=button]), select").each(function()
{
ApplyStandardBorder(this);
});
$("#"+taskContainer+r+"").find("label").each(function()
{
if(SP_Trim($(this).attr("id")) != "")
SP_RequiredLabelToggle($(this).attr("id"),false);
});
}
$.each(oVisibleTasks.value.split(","),function()
{
if(SP_Trim(this) != "")
{
SP_RemoveClass($("#"+taskContainer+this).get(0),'hide');
}
});
break;
}
switch(oTaskCounter.value*1)
{
case 0:
SP_AddClass($("#"+refSecContainer).get(0),'hide');
break;
default:
SP_RemoveClass($("#"+refSecContainer).get(0),'hide');
break;
}
if(oTaskCounter.value*1 >= totalTasks)
{
oAddTaskButton.disabled = true;
}
else
{
oAddTaskButton.disabled = false;
}
UpdateSectionHeaders(arguments[2],arguments[7]);
SP_ManipulateButtonClasses();
}
function UpdateSectionHeaders()
{
var visibleTasks = document.getElementById(arguments[0]).value.split(",");
var taskHeader = SP_Trim(arguments[1]);
var taskNo = 1;
$.each(visibleTasks,function()
{
if(SP_Trim(this) != "")
{
var oldHeader = SP_Trim($("#"+taskHeader+this).html());
var temp = oldHeader.split(" ");
var newHeader = oldHeader.replace(temp[temp.length-1],taskNo++);
$("#"+taskHeader+this).html(newHeader);
}
});
}
function DoesTaskContainData()
{
var flag = false;
$("#"+arguments[0]+"").find("input:not(input[type=button]), select").each(function()
{
if(SP_Trim($(this).val()) != "")
{
flag = true;
return false;
}
});
return flag;
}
function RemoveDataFromTask(containerID)
{
$("#"+containerID+"").find("input:not(input[type=button]), select").each(function()
{
$(this).val("");
ApplyStandardBorder($(this));
});
$("#"+containerID+"").find("label").each(function()
{
if(SP_Trim($(this).attr("id")) != "")
SP_RequiredLabelToggle($(this).attr("id"),false);
});
}
function FindLocation(visibleTasks,totalTasks)
{
var location = 1;
var tempArray = new Array();
for(i=0; i<totalTasks; i++)
{
tempArray[i] = "E";
}
$.each(visibleTasks.split(","),function()
{
if(SP_Trim(this) != "")
{
tempArray[this-1] = "F"
}
});
$.each(tempArray,function(index)
{
if(this == "E")
{
location = index+1;
return false;
}
});
return location;
}
function ApplyStandardBorder(oField)
{
if(oField != null)
{
if(oField.type == "select-one")
{
if(oField.parentNode.style.border == "thick solid red" || oField.parentNode.style.border == "red thick solid")
{
oField.parentNode.style.border = "none";
}
}
else if(oField.type == "text")
{
if(oField.style.border == "thick solid red" || oField.style.border == "red thick solid")
{
oField.style.border = "1px solid #A5C0dF";
}
}
}
}
function CopyTasksFieldValue(from,to)
{
if(to > 0 && to< from)
{
var sTaskDescrption = document.getElementById("txtCIT"+from);
var sTaskOwner = document.getElementById("mastercontrol.role.SP_COMP_TaskOwners.CITOwner"+from);
var sTaskDueDate = document.getElementById("txtCITDateDue"+from+"_date");
var sTaskDateComplete = document.getElementById("txtCITDateComplete"+from+"_date");
var sTaskReference = document.getElementById("txtCITAINo"+from);
document.getElementById("txtCIT"+to).value = SP_Trim(sTaskDescrption.value);
document.getElementById("mastercontrol.role.SP_COMP_TaskOwners.CITOwner"+to).value = sTaskOwner.value;
document.getElementById("txtCITDateDue"+to+"_date").value = SP_Trim(sTaskDueDate.value);
document.getElementById("txtCITDateComplete"+to+"_date").value = SP_Trim(sTaskDateComplete.value);
document.getElementById("txtCITAINo"+to).value = SP_Trim(sTaskReference.value);
sTaskDescrption.value = "";
sTaskOwner.selectedIndex = 0;
sTaskDueDate.value = "";
sTaskDateComplete.value = "";
sTaskReference.value = "";
}
}
function FindFirstBlankLocation(containerID)
{
var flag;
var index = -1;
for(k=1; k<11; k++)
{
flag = DoesTaskContainData(containerID+k);
if(flag == false)
{
return k;
}
}
return index;
}
function RearrangeTasks()
{
var visibleTasks = document.getElementById(arguments[0]).value;
var taskCounter = document.getElementById(arguments[1]).value*1;
var containerID = arguments[2];
var firstBlank;
var newTaskList = "";
if(taskCounter > 0)
{
$.each(visibleTasks.split(","),function()
{
if(SP_Trim(this) != "")
{
if(DoesTaskContainData(containerID+this))
{
firstBlank = FindFirstBlankLocation(containerID);
if(firstBlank > 0 && firstBlank < this)
{
CopyTasksFieldValue(this,firstBlank);
}
}
}
});
for(o=1; o<=taskCounter; o++)
{
newTaskList += o+",";
}
document.getElementById(arguments[0]).value = newTaskList;
}
}
</script>

//Following function will disable Action ITem task section fields after launch, 26-Nov-2010; Bug 27254
function DisableFieldsAfterLaunch()
{
var oRefField = document.getElementById(arguments[0]);
if(SP_Trim(oRefField.value) != "" )
{
for(var i = 1; i < arguments.length; i++)
{
document.getElementById(arguments[i]).disabled = true;
}
}
}
// adding wrokaround to execute StartupScript() because body tag is removed.
function addLoadEvent(func)
{
var oldonload = window.onload;
if (typeof window.onload != 'function')
{
window.onload = func;
}
else
{
window.onload = function()
{
if (oldonload)
{
oldonload();
}
func();
}
}
}

{
if(decisionVariable == "editform")

SP_UnrequireFields();

SP_EnableAllFields("Customer_Complaint",true);
}
}

function SetReportRequired()
{
if(REPORTEUROPE == "true")
{
var exclusionFields = ["rbIncidentOccur","rbDeficency","rbEventCaused","rbServiceLife","rbProtection","rbExpectedSideEffects","rbNegligible"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(getChecked(exclusionFields[i],0) == true)
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
if(GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListA") && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListB") && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListC") && !exclusionFlag)
{
setChecked("rbReportingRequired",0,true);
}
else
{
setChecked("rbReportingRequired",1,true);
}
}
if(REPORTCANADA == "true")
{
var exclusionFields = ["rbForeignIncidents","rbDeficiencies","rbIncidentCause","rbMalfunction","rbAbnormal","rbIncOccuring"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(SP_GetRGValue(exclusionFields[i]) == "Yes")
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
if(SP_GetRGValue("rbIncidentOccured") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbDeviceContributed") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbIncOutComes") == "Yes" && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceCQListC") && !exclusionFlag)
{
setChecked("rbCanReportingRequired",0,true);
}
else
{
setChecked("rbCanReportingRequired",1,true);
}
}
}
function ManageVigilanceQuestions(sectionName,radioName)
{
var radio_groups = {};
var flag = false;
$('#'+sectionName+'').find('input:radio').each(function(){
radio_groups[this.name] = true;
});
flag = getChecked(radioName,0);
for(group in radio_groups)
{
if(!flag)
{
$('input[name='+group+']').removeAttr('checked');
}
$('input[name='+group+']').attr('disabled', !flag);
}
}
function ManageViglanceCheckList(containerID,radioID)
{
var flag = false;
flag = getChecked(radioID,0);
$('#'+containerID).find('input:checkbox').each(function(j, items){
if(!flag)
{
$(items).attr("checked", false);
}
$(items).attr("disabled", !flag);
});
}
function EnableDisableVigilanceFields()
{
if(stepId == 1 || stepId == 3)
{
if(REPORTEUROPE == "true")
{
var exclusionFields = ["rbIncidentOccur","rbDeficency","rbEventCaused","rbServiceLife","rbProtection","rbExpectedSideEffects","rbNegligible"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(getChecked(exclusionFields[i],0) == true)
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
if(stepId == 1)
{
if(!exclusionFlag)
{
SP_PerformAction("txtJustification","disabled empty",true);
SP_GrowUP(document.getElementById("txtJustification"));
}
else
{
SP_PerformAction("txtJustification","disabled",false);
}
$("#ReportingSection").find("input:not(input[type=hidden]), select, textarea").attr("disabled",true);
}
else if(stepId == 3)
{
$("#VIGILANCETAB_EU").find("input:not(input[type=hidden]), select, textarea").attr("disabled",true);
$("#VIGILANCETAB_EU").find("input[type=button]").attr("disabled",false);
if(GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListA") && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListB") && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceQListC") && !exclusionFlag)
{
SP_PerformAction("txtDateField_date,txtReportReference","disabled",false);
var radioField = document.getElementsByName("rbTimeFrame");
for (i=0;i<radioField.length;i++)
{
radioField[i].disabled = false;
}
}
else
{
document.getElementById("txtFiling_date").value = "";
SP_PerformAction("txtDateField_date,txtReportReference","disabled empty",true);
var radioField = document.getElementsByName("rbTimeFrame");
for (i=0;i<radioField.length;i++)
{
radioField[i].checked = false;
radioField[i].disabled = true;
}
}
}
SP_ShowHideCalendar("txtDateField_date");
}
if(REPORTCANADA == "true")
{
var exclusionFields = ["rbForeignIncidents","rbDeficiencies","rbIncidentCause","rbMalfunction","rbAbnormal","rbIncOccuring"];
var exclusionFlag = false;
for(i=0; i<exclusionFields.length; i++)
{
if(SP_GetRGValue(exclusionFields[i]) == "Yes")
{
exclusionFlag = true;
break;
}
}
if(stepId == 1)
{
if(!exclusionFlag)
{
SP_PerformAction("txtVCJustification","disabled empty",true);
SP_GrowUP(document.getElementById("txtVCJustification"));
}
else
{
SP_PerformAction("txtVCJustification","disabled",false);
}
SP_EnableAllFields("ReportingForCanada",false);
}
else if(stepId == 3)
{
SP_EnableAllFields("VIGILANCETAB_CAN",false);
if(SP_GetRGValue("rbIncidentOccured") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbDeviceContributed") == "Yes" && SP_GetRGValue("rbIncOutComes") == "Yes" && GetCheckedQuestions("VigilanceCQListC") && !exclusionFlag)
{
SP_PerformAction("txtVCDateFiled_date,txtVCReportReference","disabled",false);
var radioField = document.getElementsByName("rbVCTimeFrame");
for (i=0;i<radioField.length;i++)
{
radioField[i].disabled = false;
}
}
else
{
document.getElementById("txtVCFilingDate_date").value = "";
SP_PerformAction("txtVCDateFiled_date,txtVCReportReference","disabled empty",true);
var radioField = document.getElementsByName("rbVCTimeFrame");
for (i=0;i<radioField.length;i++)
{
radioField[i].checked = false;
radioField[i].disabled = true;
}
}
}
SP_ShowHideCalendar("txtVCDateFiled_date");
}
}
}
function GetCheckedQuestions()
{
var radio_groups = {};
var totalCount = YesCount = NACount = 0;
$('#'+arguments[0]+'').find('input:radio').each(function(){
radio_groups[this.name] = true;
});
for(group in radio_groups)
{
if(getChecked(group,0) == true)
{
return true;
}
}
return false;
}
function CalculateFilingDueDate(type)
{
var days = 0;
switch(type)
{
case "EUROPE":
if(getChecked("rbTimeFrame",0) == true)
{
days = 2;
}
else if(getChecked("rbTimeFrame",1) == true)
{
days = 10;
}
else if(getChecked("rbTimeFrame",2) == true)
{
days = 30;
}
if(aDate != "")
{
date = new Date(aDate);
date.setDate(date.getDate()+days);
MC.Utils.Date.Parse({
date: date.getFullYear()+" "+(date.getMonth()+ 1)+" "+date.getDate(),
successCallback:function( result ){
document.getElementById("txtFiling_date").value = result.date;
}
});
}
else
{
document.getElementById("txtFiling_date").value = "";
}
break;
case "CANADA":
if(getChecked("rbVCTimeFrame",0) == true)
{
days = 2;
}
else if(getChecked("rbVCTimeFrame",1) == true)
{
days = 10;
}
else if(getChecked("rbVCTimeFrame",2) == true)
{
days = 30;
}
if(aDate != "")
{
date = new Date(aDate);
date.setDate(date.getDate()+days);
MC.Utils.Date.Parse({
date: date.getFullYear()+" "+(date.getMonth()+ 1)+" "+date.getDate(),
successCallback:function( result ){
document.getElementById("txtVCFilingDate_date").value = result.date;
}
});
}
else
{
document.getElementById("txtVCFilingDate_date").value = "";
}
break;
}
}
